dles preflight OPTIONS requests\n\n---\n\n## Task 11: Implement Middleware Chain Setup\n**Verifiable Output:** `pkg/workloadmanager/server/middleware/middleware.go` chains middleware\n\n- [ ] Create `middleware.go` in `pkg/workloadmanager/server/middleware/`\n- [ ] Define `Middleware` type alias: `type Middleware func(http.Handler) http.Handler`\n- [ ] Implement `Chain(middlewares ...Middleware) Middleware` function\n- [ ] Ensure correct execution order (first applied = outermost)\n- [ ] Add `Apply(h http.Handler, middlewares ...Middleware) http.Handler` helper\n- [ ] Write unit tests in `middleware_test.go`\n- [ ] Verify test: middleware executes in correct order\n- [ ] Verify test: chained middleware properly wraps handlers\n\n---\n\n## Task 12: Implement Server Options\n**Verifiable Output:** `pkg/workloadmanager/server/options.go` exists with functional options\n\n- [ ] Create `options.go` in `pkg/workloadmanager/server/`\n- [ ] Define `Option` type as function: `type Option func(*Server)`\n- [ ] Implement `WithHost(host string) Option`\n- [ ] Implement `WithPort(port int) Option`\n- [ ] Implement `WithReadTimeout(timeout time.Duration) Option`\n- [ ] Implement `WithWriteTimeout(timeout time.Duration) Option`\n- [ ] Implement `WithConfig(cfg *config.Config) Option` for bulk configuration\n- [ ] Add documentation for each option function\n\n---\n\n## Task 13: Implement HTTP Server\n**Verifiable Output:** `pkg/workloadmanager/server/server.go` exists with Server struct\n\n- [ ] Create `server.go` in `pkg/workloadmanager/server/`\n- [ ] Define `Server` struct with http.Server, router, config, logger fields\n- [ ] Implement `NewServer(opts ...Option) (*Server, error)` constructor\n- [ ] Implement `Start() error` method to start listening\n- [ ] Implement `Stop(ctx context.Context) error` for graceful shutdown\n- [ ] Implement `RegisterHandler(pattern string, handler http.Handler)` method\n- [ ] Implement `RegisterMiddleware(mw middleware.Middleware)` method\n- [ ] C